SUMMARY:The Sound of Soul – “Attune to the Wonders of God’s Unconditional Love"
DESCRIPTION:Roanoke Spiritual Experiences Group\nLocation: Roanoke ECK Center\n1420 3rd St SW\nRoanoke\, VA 24016\n\nDescription:\nExplore a daily spiritual practice for more joy\, wisdom\, peace. It can lift you to a higher state and allow you to experience more love in your life. Join us to sing HU for 15-20 minutes followed by a short contemplation and discussion.\n\nSponsored by ECKANKAR\, the Path of Spiritual Freedom.\n\nINTERNATIONAL GUESTS\, PLEASE NOTE: This event is not intended for anyone who is barred by the laws of their country from attending. Please follow the laws of your home country.
